---
title: Creamy Ranch Beef Cavatappi Skillet with White Cheddar & Scallions
description: Looking for a quick and easy dinner with a little pizzazz? This simple skillet is dressed to the nines—in ranch dressing, that is! Ground beef is cooked with our savory Ranch Spice, then swirled with cream cheese until luscious and velvety. Next, you’ll stir in tender cavatappi, sour cream, white cheddar, and buttermilk ranch dressing for an herby punch. It’s all topped off with scallions, tomatoes, and more ranch for a breezy dinner that’s dressed to impress!
